==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Polychromatic
<hw>Pol`y*chro*mat"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Poly-</ets> + <ets>chromatic</ets>.]</ety> <def>Showing a
variety, or a change, of colors.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Polychromatic acid</b></col> <fld>(Old Chem.)</fld>,
<cd>a substance obtained by the action of nitric acid on
aloes.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Polychrome</ent>⟦br⟧
